# Inline help → Tooltip (? / i)

## Display rules

| Content type | How to show |
|--------------|-------------|
| Field/label/option explanations | `HelpTooltip` or `LabelWithHelp` from `src/components/shared/HelpTooltip.tsx` |
| Validation errors | Inline `helperText` / `FormHelperText` (red), unchanged |
| Workflow guidance (multi-step) | Keep `Alert` blocks (blue/yellow), unchanged |

## Do not

- Use `helperText`, `FormHelperText`, or `Typography variant="caption"` for informational hints under fields
- Wrap entire buttons in tooltips when only the title needs help (put icon next to title instead)

## Do

- Default icon: `InfoOutlined` (`variant="info"`)
- Use `variant="help"` (`HelpOutline` / ?) when a question-style hint fits better
- Keep labels compact; full explanation on hover only
